remixlab.proscene

Class Bindings<K,A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.proscene.Bindings<K,A>

  • public class Bindings<K,A>
extends java.lang.Object
    A parameterized template class used to define shortcut bindings. This is an internal class that should not be instantiated.

    Shortcuts are mapped to keyboard and mouse actions in different places: 1. Scene global keyboard actions; 2. CameraProfile keyboard actions and mouse (and mouse-click) actions.

    Internally, this class is simply a parameterized hash-map wrap (HashMap).
